reviewText: The order was delivered on time, but two of the dvd`s did not work on any player that I have. The one that did work was interesting and of good quality. Mostly for showmanship as opposed to martial application. Not my cup of tea and didn`t bother to file complaint due to the low price and did not want to spend time on it. I gave it to my son and said enjoy if you like it or give to someone that you think may.
